reviews.text: Dine in here for two nights when I was visiting Hong Kong. Great food and excellent service. Would recommend to tourist. But the restautant it self is pretty hard to find for the first time. Must try.

I have been tried a lots of Thai food restaurant in Hong Kong. I could say the taste which presented to costumer is the almost 100% like traditional Thai food in Thailand. Especially the taste of the spicy crab is quite similar the one I tried in Bangkok before. Will come back again!

A good quality food, but less tasty than in other thai restaurants. The beef was super. The restaurant is a quite small place but the view is really nice. Check the mall map before you go, it is a pretty hard to find.
Had an excellent Thai food experience there... Looking forward to visit again
Good food. Nice environment. Recommend!

reviews.text: Nice ambience. The reception told us that a minimum charge of HKD 1000 for a table when we has no reservation. It was not along the window side. Food was good. Service was alright but not great. The bar  has good view but was very crowded  though.

Very bad. Ordered crispy fish and after 20min of waiting they came to tell they don't have it. Ordered another type of fish and after 10min they told they don't have it either. Spring rolls were really oily and heavy, as was the soft shell crab. AND THEY CHARGED SEPARATELY FOR THE NUTS! Nice harbor view but everything else sucked. Too touristic!
Very warm, polite and caring staff. Very good food quality. Have a good view of the world famous Victoria Harbour.  I love this restaurant.
Great view. Food is ok. Connected to the eyebar.
Pricey for what it is but undeniably gorgeous views of the  Hong Kong habour. The service is alright too. There are some fun twists to dishes. We came here twice in the same week.

reviews.text:
維港view，茶餐廳水準嘅服務

Excellent view, satisfactory food, poor service due to poor training......

同三個朋友食lunch，坦白講我極少嚟呢種餐廳食飯，去酒店餐廳就多少少經驗，但唔使同同級比較都知服務有幾差......

食物唔算大問題，預咗嚟食景，問題係啲侍應嘅質素，一坐低就sell你叫杯蔗汁羅漢果茶，但凍熱都落錯，幫你加茶時就有兩滴茶倒落碟餸度......
